drm/radeon: use kzalloc for allocating one thing

Use kzalloc for allocating one thing rather than
kcalloc(1...

The semantic patch that makes this change is as follows:

// <smpl>
@@
@@

- kcalloc(1,
+ kzalloc(
          ...)
// </smpl>

